rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I've tried to get to Iyasaki Village many times,
but I keep failing, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I slip off the path,
fall into the Cloud Sea,
swim, and climb up...

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I was found by a Fleet Moramora
and almost eaten...

rows.label: tlk42350162_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I somehow managed to pry its mouth open
and escape, mo! Esasa is not food, mo!!
